description:
In this course, we will cover:

  • Setting goals and achieving them
  • Nutrition - what to eat, how much, and what to avoid
  • Training - Specifics of working out, including weight and cardiovascular training, as well as their benefits
  • Supplements - what they are, what you need to know if considering using them, and what I recommend.

Throughout your journey, I will be here answering ANY question you may have!

Good luck with your transformation, and I really look forward to working with you!
title: Bodybuilding 101
